function REDUCE(key, list_of_values):
    sum = 0
    for v in list_of_values: sum += v
    EMIT(key, sum)</div>
<p><span class="kh">Data locality</span> means each mapper runs on the node where its data chunk already resides — avoiding costly network transfer.</p>
