<div class="ans-card"><div class="ans-head"><span>NoSQL — Complete with Graph Database Comparison (Neo4j vs OrientDB)</span><span class="marks20">20 Marks</span></div>
<div class="ans-body">
<p>NoSQL ("<span class="kh">Not Only SQL</span>") databases are <span class="kh">schema-less</span> and <span class="kh">horizontally scalable</span>, built to handle the variety and volume of Big Data that rigid RDBMS structures cannot.</p>
